{"tid":1878601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳健波出任行政總裁的立橋保險 : 捐100萬俾工聯會起口罩生產線","createTime":"2020-02-13T17:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T19:48:58.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"13eef80a8bccbe31cecd55617d1a13e76166f37c","tid":1878601,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"由立法會財委會主席陳健波出任行政總裁的立橋保險集團，今天宣佈撥出100萬元予工聯會職業發展服務處，以讓工聯會建立本地口罩生產線。公司指口罩會在本港自設的符合衛生標準的廠房生產，標明是「香港製造 Made in HK」的口罩，製成品會送贈長者、基層家庭及有需要人士<br />\n<br />\n500 萬經中聯辦支援湖北省<br />\n<br />\n立橋在上月底宣佈捐出 1000 萬元支援新冠狀病毒抗疫行動，一半即 500 萬元支援本港抗疫工作，成立生產口罩線撥出的 100 萬元就是從這筆款項而來。而另一半款項 500 萬元則支援湖北省，包括武漢在內的抗疫工作，公司今日已通過香港中聯辦的賑災專戶捐款贈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E5%81%A5%E6%B3%A2%E4%BB%BB-ceo-%E7%AB%8B%E6%A9%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA-100-%E8%90%AC%E8%B4%88%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E4%25BB%25BB-ceo-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA-100-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B4%2588%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%2F&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvUzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=045a90d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2581%25A5%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E4%25BB%25BB-ceo-%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%259A%25AA-100-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B4%2588%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%2F&h=97028d88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%99%B3%E5%81%A5%E6%B3%A2%E4%BB%BB-ceo-%E7%AB%8B%E6%A9%8B%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%AA-100-%E8%90%AC%E8%B4%88%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9/</a>"},{"pid":"e68c0a2bc23c4a5005dd550e171